Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.09,0:01:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺留下來的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.40,0:01:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到對方竟然自己送上門來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將以這一擊 回歸那懷念的歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.11,0:01:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.13,0:01:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.91,0:01:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠距離攻擊魔法 準備術式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.69,0:01:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備術式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.04,0:01:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令官 隨同部隊傳來聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.32,0:02:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里曼機關的騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.08,0:02:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以第一先遣隊的指揮官為人質
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要求與司令官對話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.59,0:02:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊 在這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.36,0:02:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫他有話等結束再說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.74,0:02:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一先遣隊的指揮權移交給副官
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續作戰行動 就這樣回覆過去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.51,0:02:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.64,0:02:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等這天等得好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.08,0:02:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能被些瑣碎雜事打擾到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.53,0:02:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一擊 準備
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.67,0:02:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一擊 準備完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.76,0:02:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開炮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.69,0:02:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展開防禦魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯現吧 攔截者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.36,0:03:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Interceptor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發動攻擊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.72,0:03:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒多少時間了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也有看門狗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.48,0:03:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始攻擊了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.55,0:03:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤特拉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.96,0:03:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面似乎就算放棄你也要繼續作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人不是工具
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺身守護君主部下領民才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.14,0:03:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你玷污了我作為先鋒的榮譽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對饒不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.09,0:03:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷下方中彈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,損傷確認中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何索厄拉的攻擊能擊穿我方防禦魔法?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是該我們佔優的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:03:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想來只可能是裝載的魔法思念料的差距…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.12,0:04:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續 不要減緩攻擊力度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念料的純度可是不同的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻對面陣腳大亂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討伐軍 對我們來說不過是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往首都的礙腳石而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像開打了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過有魔法防壁在 應該不至於立即被擊墜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 你情況怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神支配的術式應該已經解除了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎我該道聲謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.70,0:04:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 我們也是因時勢才如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你這句話我輕鬆許多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再相遇 可以毫不顧忌地殺掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.74,0:05:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.79,0:05:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大致說明下現在情況
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我基本都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有意識 也有記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.30,0:05:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵抗不住想受敵人支配的強烈欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此不舒服的感受我還是第一次經歷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫葛拉特的魔法師 我必須要好好謝他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 比起這事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼下更重要的是兄長和嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯 肯定沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿卡莉也…芙蕾多妮卡也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺體 回收
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回歸 和大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 加瓦爾尼公爵家的人們已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.63,0:06:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 里加爾圖自身言明已把所有人殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.04,0:06:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿卡莉?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是芙蕾多妮卡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:06:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你縮小了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:06:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我脫皮了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫皮?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是輸了一次嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.83,0:07:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我汲取教訓 把身體改為了雙重構造
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這樣保溫性也好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.77,0:07:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你誰呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.31,0:07:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 托魯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長往最頂層去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡也在最上面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想盡快與兄長他們匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.05,0:07:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拜託你嗎 順便帶上她們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這荒唐的生物到底是怎麼回事啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央部中彈 魔法機關受損
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法維持平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要膽怯 開炮 開炮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.29,0:08:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基烈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑 李奧納多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:08:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基烈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基烈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊魔法失去準頭了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎發射口中彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若這樣 即使到了首都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.64,0:09:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也無法發動魔法攻擊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里加爾圖大人 葛拉特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.77,0:09:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想到了個辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼辦法? 告訴我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這要塞本身當作炮彈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.45,0:09:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對維馬克王宮發起突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.59,0:09:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並發動魔法自爆怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.55,0:09:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有索厄拉的魔法力在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應能將整個卡多威爾夷為平地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這主意不錯 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們自身成為新戰爭的導火索
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在歷史上留下痕跡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若維馬克王國遭遇實際上的滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.15,0:09:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個大陸都會陷入混亂的漩渦中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.41,0:09:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是蕾拉 你總會為我們指明道路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為里加爾圖大人和葛拉特大人的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉獻上一切就是我的喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時 也是我的復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合軍的航天要塞已處於毀滅狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們繼續前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.21,0:10:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著首都卡多威爾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.92,0:10:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 別想全身而退
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.42,0:10:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然回歸王國無望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.05,0:10:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也要拉你們一起上路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.41,0:10:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 上升
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.65,0:10:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將剩餘的功率全都使出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡 在就回話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁斷皇帝阿圖爾·賈茲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用雙手創造了歷史的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:11:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了明天 我也能與他比肩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.77,0:11:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賈茲皇帝的願望 也會由我的雙手…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.57,0:11:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽了我的話 還有逃跑的力氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼想要這遺體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 原來入侵者是你們呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是第一次見到蕾拉以外的「嘉依卡」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.33,0:12:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是里加爾圖·加瓦爾尼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.52,0:12:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你父親的信徒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.63,0:12:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好期待 竟有幸親手切割「嘉依卡」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停 停止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一眨眼就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.47,0:12:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這要塞將突入首都卡多威爾自爆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺體也好 「嘉依卡」也好 都會化為灰燼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是命運
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.84,0:12:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否定 放棄 否定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.74,0:12:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯 會來 必定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為鋼也
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 嘉依卡剛才還在這兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面就是司令室了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這群傢伙到底有多少隻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有殺過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著慢著 讓我來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得報剛才的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡 你在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像有點累?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.88,0:14:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的內臟是什麼顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 輸了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那不是戰鬥 你只是用刀在刺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.41,0:14:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 這就是生命嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想弄明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.29,0:14:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來只要自己死一次 就能明白了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯 傷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無大礙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 趕緊回收遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.55,0:14:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然撞了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:14:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是糾纏不休
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.64,0:15:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎負責操縱的魔法師被打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.73,0:15:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的達成了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.31,0:15:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來只剩如何逃離這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.19,0:15:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:15:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:15:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍舊尋求遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你的答覆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.90,0:16:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你接受自己工具的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就作為工具腐朽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Salimic binnu allay
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.81,0:16:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯現吧 強擊者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Slugger
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.95,0:17:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Floater
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.56,0:17:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.96,0:17:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯 救助成功
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.61,0:17:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什麼鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我說多少次 亂破師只是僱主的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人為工具而冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.71,0:17:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可謂本末倒置…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.35,0:17:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否定 托魯 工具 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.03,0:18:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工具 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長 嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿卡莉 芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索厄拉 在下沉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.19,0:18:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉 很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管你幫了我們那麼多…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.09,0:18:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 里加爾圖大人和葛拉特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願意陪我復仇至今
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很感激
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.71,0:19:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能成為賈茲皇帝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有些累了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也累了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.27,0:19:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的活法 我的死法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我自己選的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.86,0:19:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定讓基烈特大人擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然空手而歸…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.54,0:19:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是該活捉嘉依卡回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.81,0:19:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇 芷依塔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.24,0:19:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋了 怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基烈特大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.08,0:20:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我跟著還…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.28,0:20:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基烈特大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別嚇我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是在騙我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇 隊長他…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人 騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人騙人 你們騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.46,0:20:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不信 不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.36,0:20:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…你們騙人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.86,0:20:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 薇薇 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被創造的存在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.17,0:20:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若這是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.24,0:20:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼「收集遺體」本身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是某人為達到目的而設計的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.05,0:20:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 那你自己想怎麼辦啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:21:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺體 收集 繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.59,0:21:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 其他沒有 什麼都
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.94,0:21:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺體 收集 想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.25,0:21:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和托魯 和阿卡莉 和芙蕾多妮卡 一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決意不變
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.55,0:21:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.27,0:21:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,協助 可能?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還講這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我選你為主人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.99,0:21:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你是假貨還是被人利用 這都無關
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.82,0:21:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我與兄長一心同體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會追隨到天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.17,0:21:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你乾脆和我簽契約算了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.20,0:21:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若今後還要這樣亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.17,0:21:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆和我簽訂契約 成為龍騎士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.58,0:21:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不用一一療傷了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.31,0:21:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說笑呢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.31,0:21:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會考慮的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.44,0:21:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.47,0:21:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若要出發還是趁早吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.35,0:22:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定基烈特小隊會追來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.41,0:22:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.12,0:22:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新英雄 喜好葡萄酒 美魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.91,0:23:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 魔法技術 本領了得
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.27,0:23:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 托魯 阿卡莉 苦戰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.42,0:23:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 敗退?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.75,0:23:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 收集遺體的皇女
