Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.61,0:01:13.86,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}即使是拼湊的時光又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.18,0:01:20.25,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}向左向右都通向告別 這種答案毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.42,0:01:25.43,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我只會繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:29.05,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}直到遇見你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.59,0:22:22.92,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}行屍走肉般走過的路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:28.43,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}頭頂的陽光分外刺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.54,0:22:33.64,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}不知何時你已經淪落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.05,0:22:39.35,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}連自己名字也都遺忘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.30,0:22:43.56,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}究竟人類 為何而活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.01,0:22:47.23,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}哪怕生命 流逝消磨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.79,0:22:51.14,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}這無盡的煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.91,0:22:55.85,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}不如隨之起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:22:56.84,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}無常之花
